Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:35.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪やることだらけで\Nテンパって、
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.70,0:23:35.95,Planetes - ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}{\blur1}yaru koto darake de tenpatte
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.70,0:23:35.95,Planetes - ED,,0,0,20,,{\fad(0,200)}{\an2\blur1}Even if life's so hectic that our tempers flare,
