Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:49.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪気楽にいこうぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.40,0:23:49.40,Planetes - ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}{\blur1}kiraku ni ikou ze
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.40,0:23:49.40,Planetes - ED,,0,0,20,,{\fad(0,200)}{\an2\blur1}Let's move on without a care in our hearts.
